 Lady Hawk heard Najah returning from outside and quickly rushed back 
to her lab. It was better that nobody reported her wandering the ship 
or Zardus might reconsider her worth to him. she returned to her 
research knowing that Zardus would want a sample of her work. He 
could walk in on her at any time and expect a sample at a moments 
notice.

OOC for future reference can Najah order a lockdown of the lab or 
does Zardus have to do it?
